  "body": "While Status Desktop and the catalogue app will be the main driver and probably only consumers of the library for now, we should have a proper release process so that consuming the library can be done in a predictable manner.\r\n\r\nThings we should do:\r\n\r\n- Follow SemVer\r\n- Automatically release changelogs based on commit messages\r\n- Ideally have a proper testing story to ensure components are working correctly (this could be a later step though)\r\n\r\nI think the easiest thing we can do for now is put up a simple script that uses something like `clog`, and a little bit of git-fu. ",
